# Tokens docvet's heuristics flag that are correct as written. One per line.
# Everything here was triaged by hand — if a token belongs in this file, the
# reason it is a false positive belongs next to it, or the list rots into a
# blanket mute and the tool stops being worth running.

# Brace-expansion shorthand for a set of sibling files. Every expansion exists;
# docvet resolves the literal string, which never will.
internal/parser/{go,js,python,shell,rust,ruby}.go
cmd/runecho-guard/{dangling,duplicate,filescope,qualified,depqualified,contract}.go

# Placeholder paths in copy-paste examples. Deliberately not real.
/path/to/your/repo
/path/to/worktree
/path/to/source
YOUR_USER

# Claude Code slash commands, not URL routes.
/plugin

# Directory references in prose, read as routes by the URL heuristic.
/internal/snapshot/
/internal/parser

# direnv's config file, named in a troubleshooting note. Not a code symbol,
# and this repo does not use direnv itself.
.envrc
